Responsibilities

  Responsible for the overall operation of an assigned building(s) and surrounding compound
  Responsible for the management, supervision and coordination of all maintenance contractors assigned 
  Handle renewal of term contracts and administration of contractual records

Requirements:

  Degree / Diploma in Building / Real Estate Management or other related discipline in facility management
  Must possess valid Fire Safety Manager certificate
  Minimum 8 years’ relevant experience
  Strong verbal and written communication skills in English and Mandarin in order to converse with local contractors and be able to translate documents
  Strictly only SINGAPOREANS need apply
